This template sets up a {{tl|Таксобокс}}, a table setting out the [[Biological classification]] ([[taxonomy]]) for a group of living things with a choice of over 135 parameters.  Although the implementation is complicated, it is relatively simple to use.  For an example in practice, look at the edit page of [[killer whale]]&nbsp;– [{{fullurl:Killer whale|action=edit}}].  Most parameters are optional, so if a particular entry is not relevant for your case, just leave it out.

This guide has come out of [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Tree of life|WikiProject Tree of life]].

